text: Parmish Verma (born 3 July 1990) is an Indian singer, rapper, music video director, videographer and actor associated with the Punjabi Music and Punjabi cinema. He started his career as a video director then singer, and later debuted as an actor with the film Rocky Mental. == References == Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Indian singers Category:Indian actors Category:Punjabi people
